                                <p>
                                    Rhod's vexed by the lamentable fashion in ladies' eyebrows, where they are plucked beyond recognition. The trend's even reached the Royal household. And Lloyd's after alternative suggestions to Winston Churchill for the back of the new five pound note; would a paintball fight between Bob Holness and Pat Sharp fit the (literal) bill?
